{"title":"磨坊","authors":["郭良原"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨坊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭良原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经被白色的纸条封闭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被当作制造毒菌的工厂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布满尘垢和蛛网的磨架上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搁着两盘冰冷的石头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搁着两盘沉重的凄凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有穿过破壁的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有蛇和老鼠闪着绿光的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它没有了生命的挑战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也停止了劳动的歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于有一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个年轻的后生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起了历史铸造的锯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锯断了它门上的锈锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将一张写着“包”字的告示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴在向着太阳的地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨声象一支熟悉的村歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘荡出古老的音韵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘荡出复苏的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村子中央的磨坊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一尊平原与人浑然一体的雕像。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}